<P>A BRIEF VINDICATION OF THE PARTICULAR COMMUNION OF THE <HI>BAPTIST CHURCHES:</HI> BEING A REPLY to the REMARKS <HI>OF</HI> The Rev. <HI>NOAH WORCESTER,</HI> A. B. IN A "FRIENDLY LETTER" to the <HI>Author.</HI> WHEREIN THE SUBJECTS <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> ARE PARTICULARLY CONSIDERED.</P>
<P>BY THOMAS BALDWIN, PASTOR OF THE SECOND BAPTIST CHURCH IN BOSTON.</P>
