<P>In page 19, 2d paragraph, in&s;tead of the three fir&s;t lines, read as follows:&mdash;<HI>If indeed it be evident from &s;cripture, "That none but &s;uch, who are thus vi&s;ibly, and in the charitable judgment of the church, believe<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">,"</HI> &amp;c.</P>
